The paper deals with video classification, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed method involves attention mechanisms and non-linear transforms, which are common techniques in machine learning (cs.MM) and deep learning (cs.LG). The paper also mentions the use of large-scale datasets, which could fall under information retrieval (cs.IR) or natural language processing (cs.CL) subcategories.
